<p>Let Pastor Craig lead your discussion with this week‚Äôs video. Also, find this video on Roku, Apple TV, Android TV, Fire TV, and <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5ZNyRTYc_sY">YouTube</a></p>

